## 🎯 Project Objectives

- Develop a **non-contact wound measurement system** using structured light.
- Project and capture a **laser-line profile** over the wound surface.
- Implement **FPGA-based real-time laser stripe extraction** and image processing.
- Reconstruct the wound profile in **3D** using triangulation principles.
- Estimate **wound depth, surface area, and approximate volume**.
- Provide a **telemedicine-ready dashboard** for visualization and remote triage support.

